disable Nightrazor and prevent him from escaping the Ark as he would hope to 
do.  Straight Shot&#39;s thoughts were to strike in an area which would 
definitely stop Nightrazor.  She probes with her thermal sensing equipment, 
hoping to find a spot in his spinal servos.
Tucson concentrates as well, realizing that perhaps a spinal shot would be 
best.  He narrows an optic, and also senses a spot as well.  He concentrates 
on an area where there appears to be an opening and meets Straight Shot&#39;s 
intentions perfectly.

&quot;Right.  It won&#39;t kill him, but it will disable him. Let&#39;s hope this works. 
